ses%2C%20and%20some%20modernized%20older%20systems.%20Though%20only%20semi-integrated%20compared%20to%20fully%20networked%20air%20defenses%2C%20it%20presented%20an%20obstacle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20dismantled%20Iranian%20defenses%20over%20multiple%20engagements%20through%20extensive%20planning%2C%20detailed%20intelligence%2C%20and%20the%20employment%20of%20combat-proven%20airpower%2C%20specifically%20fifth-generation%20F-35%20stealth%20fighters%20built%20for%20penetration%20and%20suppression%20of%20enemy%20air%20defenses%20and%20fourth-generation%20F-15s%20and%20F-16s%2C%20which%20can%20also%20support%20that%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImportant%20to%20Israel's%20success%20in%20the%20latest%20fight%20with%20Iran%20were%20the%20engagements%20last%20year%20that%20substantially%20weakened%20Iranian%20air%20defense%20capabilities%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Israel's%20skills%20in%20this%20mission.%20Failures%20and%20aircraft%20losses%20in%20the%201973%20Yom%20Kippur%20War%20led%20it%20to%20reevaluate%20how%20it%20approached%20enemy%20air%20defenses%2C%20in%20many%20ways%20leading%20to%20the%20emergence%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20missions%20used%20against%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEd%20Arnold%2C%20a%20security%20expert%20at%20RUSI%2C%20said%20that%20Israel%20reporting%20no%20aircraft%20losses%20%26quot%3Bwas%20significant%2C%20and%20it%20just%20showed%20that%2C%20yeah%2C%20you%20can%20get%20air%20supremacy%20very%20quickly.%26quot%3B%20The%20caveat%20there%20is%20that%20doing%20so%20requires%20the%20right%20tactics%2C%20weapons%2C%20and%20intelligence%2C%20but%20even%20then%2C%20it%20is%20not%20guaranteed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetired%20Air%20Commodore%20Andrew%20Curtis%2C%20an%20airfare%20expert%20with%20a%2035-year%20career%20in%20the%20Royal%20Air%20Force%2C%20told%20BI%20%26quot%3Bthe%20situation%20that%20everybody's%20been%20used%20to%20over%20the%20last%2030%20years%20is%20air%20supremacy%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20high-intensity%20war%20against%20a%20near-pe