0public%20servants%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20in%20March%20aimed%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-limits-public-service-loan-forgiveness-program-pslf-education-department-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elimiting%20the%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20created%20in%202007%20to%20forgive%20student%20debt%20for%20government%20and%20nonprofit%20workers%20after%2010%20years%20of%20qualifying%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20unclear%20which%20specific%20organizations%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20many%20borrowers%20%E2%80%94%20could%20lose%20PSLF%20eligibility%2C%20the%20executive%20order%20signaled%20that%20organizations%20facilitating%20transgender%20healthcare%20or%20engaging%20in%20disability%20discrimination%2C%20which%20the%20administration%20defined%20as%20%26quot%3Banti-American%26quot%3B%20activities%2C%20could%20be%20on%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20question%20dominated%20the%20discussion%20during%20negotiation%20sessions%20that%20took%20place%20on%20June%2030%20through%20July%202%2C%20during%20which%20representatives%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20met%20with%20a%20range%20of%20stakeholders%20to%20help%20craft%20new%20language%20for%20PSLF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20draft%20of%20the%20department's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ed.gov%2Fmedia%2Fdocument%2F2025-pslf-discussion-paper-final-day-3-070225-final-version-consensus-110363.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproposal%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20change%20PSLF%2C%20circulated%20among%20negotiators%2C%20shed%20more%20light%20on%20how%20the%20administration%20seeks%20to%20change%20the%20debt%20relief%20program.%20Specifically%2C%20the%20proposal%20includes%20revising%20the%20definition%20of%20a%20qualifying%20employer%20%26quot%3Bto%20ensure%20that%20organizations%20that%20engage%20in%20activities%20that%20have%20a%20substantial%20illegal%20purpose%26quot%3B%20are%20not%20eligible%20for%20PSLF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20illegal%20purposes%2C%20per%20the%20proposal%2C%20include%20discrimination%2C%20like%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20federal%20disabilities%20act%3B%20violations%20of%20federal%20immigration%20law%3B%20what%20the%20department%20characterizes%20as%20%26quot%3Bchemical%20castration%20or%20mutilation%2C%26quot%3B%20like%20the%20use%20of%20puberty%20blockers%20or%20hormones%20to%20help%20a%20transgender%20person%20transition%3B%20and%20acts%20of%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20education%20secretary%20would%20determine%20if%20an%20employer%20has%20engaged%20in%20any%20of%20those%20activities%20on%20or%20after%20July%201%2C%202026.%20If%20the%20secretary%20finds%20any%20violations%2C%20payments%20a%20borrower%20made%20toward%20PSLF%20while%20working%20for%20the%20ineligible%20employer%20would%20not%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20negotiators%20on%20the%20committee%20expressed%20concerns%20with%20making%20changes%20to%20the%20PSLF%20eligibility%20criteria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20see%20where%20the%20secretary%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20remove%20the%20employer%20eligibility%20definition%2C%26quot%3B%20Betsy%20Mayotte%2C%20the%20president%20of%20The%20Institute%20of%20Student%20Loan%20Advisors%20and%20a%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Erepresentative%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%2C%20said%20during%20a%20session.%20She%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bthese%20jobs%20are%20essential%20to%20the%20communities%20that%20they%20serve.%20So%20the%20intent%20of%20Congress%20was%20not%20to%20narrow%20the%20eligibility.%20It%20was%20to%20make%20it%20as%20expansive%20as%20possible%20under%20the%20statute%20that%20they%20wrote.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacob%20Lallo%2C%20a%20general%20attorney%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20broad%20rulemaking%20power%20for%20the%20secretary%20to%20promulgate%20regulations%20that%20interpret%20statutes.%20That%20is%20a%20long-standing%20part%20of%20American%20agency%20and%20administrative%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20negotiations%20have%20concluded%2C%20the%20committee%20ultimately%20did%20not%20reach%20consensus%2C%20and%20any%20changes%20will%20take%20time%20to%20become%20finalized.%20As%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20works%20on%20the%20final%20text%20to%20amend%20PSLF%2C%20there%20will%20be%20more%20opportunities%20for%20public%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20proud%20that%20the%20committee%20members%20representing%20institutions%20of%20higher%20education%2C%20veterans%2C%20taxpayers%2C%20borrowers%2C%20and%20the%20business%20community%20have%20helped%20fulfill%20one%20of%20President%20Trump's%20promises%20to%20ensure%20that%20PSLF%20does%20not%20subsidize%20organizations%20that%20are%20breaking%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Acting%20Under%20Secretary%20of%20Education%20James%20Bergeron%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHave%20a%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aasheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cb096767-3b87-494c-9edf-5e5b4d66a8f3%5C%22%3E'Borrowers%20organized%20entire%20careers%20around%20this%20promise'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20negotiators%20raised%20the%20alarm%20on%20establishing%20new%20definitions%20in%20areas%20that%20are%20not%20directly%20related%20to%20student%20loans%2C%20like%20the%20clause%20seeking%20to%20include%20the%20use%20of%20puberty%20blockers%20as%20an%20example%20of%20chemical%20castration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20that%20the%20folks%20assembled%20to%20be%20part%20of%20this%20rulemaking%20were%20assembled%20for%20their%20medical%20expertise%2C%26quot%3B%20Abby%20Shafroth%2C%20a%20representative%20from%20the%20Student%20Loan%20Borrower%20Assistance%20Project%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20we're%20here%20with%20student%20loan%20expertise%2C%20and%20so%20I%20would%20feel%20very%20uncomfortable%20setting%20a%20new%20legal%20definition%20for%20these%20medical%20terms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENegotiators%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20maintained%20that%20the%20intent%20of%20limiting%20PSLF%20is%20not%20to%20completely%20overhaul%20the%20program%3B%20it's%20to%20ensure%20that%20those%20participating%20in%20the%20program%20have%20employers%20who%20are%20delivering%20a%20public%20service%20to%20the%20American%20public.%20The%20proposal%20would%20also%20allow%20employers%20that%20the%20secretary%20determines%20to%20be%20ineligible%20for%20PSLF%20to%20respond%20to%20and%20challenge%20the%20department's%20findings%20before%20a%20final%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20original%20executive%20order%20said%20that%20PSLF%20has%20previously%20%26quot%3Bmisdirected%20tax%20dollars%20into%20activist%20organizations%20that%20not%20only%20fail%20to%20serve%20the%20public%20interest%2C%20but%20actually%20harm%20our%20national%20security%20and%20American%20values%2C%20sometimes%20through%20criminal%20means.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20did%20not%20provide%20specific%20examples%20of%20those%20activities%2C%20leaving%20some%20borrowers%20who%20rely%20on%20the%20program%20on%20edge.%20One%20borrower%20advocate%2C%20who%20spoke%20during%20the%20public%20comment%20period%20of%20negotiations%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20are%20paralyzed%20by%20anxiety%20because%20rules%20keep%20shifting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBorrowers%20organized%20entire%20careers%20around%20this%20promise%2C%20and%20now%20they%20live%20in%20constant%20fear%20of%20the%20next%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20currently%20proposed%20barriers%20will%20do%20little%20to%20stop%20wrongdoing%2C%20but%20will%20create%20enormous%20administrative%20burden.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers