nam.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20lowered%20tariffs%20on%20Vietnam%20to%2020%25%20but%20is%20slapping%2040%25%20tariffs%20on%20transshipments%20through%20the%20country.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EVietnam%20has%20benefited%20from%20supply-chain%20shifts%20due%20to%20US-China%20trade%20tensions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20gave%20Vietnam%20a%20trade%20break%20%E2%80%94%20and%20used%20it%20to%20squeeze%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fchina%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChina.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Trump%20announced%20a%20trade%20deal%20with%20Hanoi%20that%20would%20levy%2020%25%20on%20imports%20from%20Vietnam%2C%20down%20from%20the%2046%25%20rate%20Trump%20announced%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-liberation-day-reciprocal-tariffs-speech-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20In%20return%2C%20Vietnam%20has%20agreed%20to%20allow%20American%20goods%20to%20enter%20the%20country%20duty-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20also%20significant%20is%20that%20Trump%20announced%20a%2040%25%20tariff%20on%20goods%20shipped%20from%20another%20country%20via%20Vietnam%20to%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20a%20move%20that%20analysts%20say%20is%20aimed%20squarely%20at%20transshipments%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20'China%20quotient'%20in%20US%20negotiations%20with%20other%20Asian%20economies%20is%20arguably%20evident%20in%20the%20deal%20with%20Vietnam%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Vishnu%20Varathan%2C%20Mizuho's%20macro%20research%20head%20for%20Asia%2C%20excluding%20Japan%2C%20in%20a%20Thursday%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US's%20intent%20is%20quite%20obviously%20to%20not%20disincentivize%20Vietnam's%20role%20as%20a%20substitute%20for%20China%20at%20a%20lower%2020%25%20tariff%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVietnam%20has%20benefited%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-trade-war-covid-companies-moving-supply-chains-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eglobal%20supply-chain%20shifts%3C%2Fa%3E%20away%20from%20China%20since%20Trump's%20initial%20trade%20war%20during%20his%20first%20term.%20In%20response%20to%20those%20tariffs%2C%20many%20multinational%20companies%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-supply-chains-moving-companies-outside-mainland-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChinese%20firms%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20moved%20manufacturing%20operations%20to%20lower-cost%20hubs%20like%20Vietnam%20to%20sidestep%20US%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20US%20ran%20a%20%24123.5%20billion%20trade%20deficit%20with%20Vietnam%2C%20making%20it%20America's%20third-largest%20trade%20gap%20after%20China%20and%20Mexico%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%20Trade%20Representative's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fcffd6ac-e0dc-42f2-8080-d0c2551fec7f%5C%22%3EA%20model%20for%20future%20trade%20deals%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20follows%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-china-trade-deal-agreement-slash-trump-tariffs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etemporary%20truce%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20Washington%20and%20Beijing%20in%20May%2C%20when%20both%20sides%20agreed%20to%20a%2090-day%20pause%20in%20their%20tariff%20war.%20The%20US%20slashed%20duties%20on%20Chinese%20goods%20from%20145%25%20to%2030%25%2C%20while%20China%20lowered%20its%20tariffs%20on%20American%20imports%20from%20125%25%20to%2010%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20transshipment%20tariff%20on%20Vietnam%20underscores%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20effort%20to%20close%20the%20backdoor%20for%20Chinese%20exporters%20seeking%20loopholes%20into%20the%20US%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20tariff%20framework%20that%20targets%20transshipment%20while%20preserving%20the%20potential%20benefits%20of%20efficient%20cross-border%20commerce%20is%20a%20smart%20move%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20model%20for%20future%20trade%20deals%20%E2%80%94%20if%20enforced%20transparently%20and%20paired%20with%20clear%20rules%20of%20origin%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Eli%20Clemens%2C%20a%20policy%20analyst%20at%20Washington-based%20Information%20Technology%20and%20Innovation%20Foundation%2C%20a%20nonpartisan%20research%20institute%2C%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20also%20shows%20that%20Washington%20can%20stop%20Chinese%20supply%20chains%20from%20extending%20themselves%20into%20Southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFuture%20trade%20negotiations%20should%20also%20include%20targeted%20transshipment%20deterrents%20that%20level%20the%20playing%20field%20for%20US%20manufacturers%20and%20retailers%2C%26quot%3B%20Clemens%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221f690ef8-0938-4b8c-a134-c5fa5be2bb0c%5C%22%3EAsia%20in%20a%20bind%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWashington's%20focus%20on%20transshipment%20enforcement%20puts%20pressure%20on%20other%20Asian%20economies%2C%20which%20may%20find%20themselves%20forced%20to%20choose%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20remiss%20to%20ignore%20this%20critical%20pillar%20of%20US%20trade%20deals%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20Asia%2C%20which%20is%20trained%20on%20undermining%20China's%20economic%20reach%20and%20influence%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Varathan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20may%20also%20reinforce%20Beijing's%20view%20that%20US%20trade%20negotiations%20lacks%20%26quot%3Bgood%20faith.%26quot%3B%20It%20could%20prompt%20retaliation%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20against%20the%20US%2C%20but%20also%20against%20Asian%20economies%20seen%20as%20siding%20with%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOther%20Asian%20economies%20will%20be%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20a%20two-sided%20geoeconomic%20squeeze%20given%20that%20their%20reliance%20on%20both%20China%20and%20US%20are%20significant%2C%26quot%3B%20Varathan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20reservations%20about%20the%20deal%2C%20it%20still%20excited%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fnasdaq_100%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENasdaq%20Composite%3C%2Fa%3E%20soared%20to%20record%20highs%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20US%20stock%20futures%20are%20extending%20gains%20early%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVietnam's%20widely%20followed%20VN-Index%20also%20rose%20to%20its%20highest%20level%20since%20April%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-trade-tariff-deal-vietnam-target-china-transshipment-supply-chain-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751522636000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686621d43d5881a51c1c9ce1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-trade-tariff-deal-vietnam-target-china-transshipment-supply-chain-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Donald%20Trump%20announced%20a%20trade%20deal%20with%20Hanoi%20that%20would%20levy%2020%25%20on%20imports%20and%20a%2040%25%20tariff%20on%20transshipment%20from%20Vietnam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A117%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-trade-tariff-deal-vietnam-target-china-transshipment-supply-chain-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22June%20Services%20PMI%20touches%2010-month%20high%20at%2060.4%20on%20sharp%20upturn%20in%20new%20biz%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751522349000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.co