.%20Ajay%20emphasises%20making%20brief%2C%20to-the-point%20notes%20that%20encapsulate%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20topics%2C%20ensuring%20that%20complex%20information%20can%20be%20quickly%20recalled.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20where%20I%20was%20lagging%20in%20Geography%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20I%20made%20the%20mistake%20of%20not%20making%20concise%20notes%2C%20and%20at%20the%20end%2C%20I%20had%20massive%20and%20cluttered%20notes%2C%20which%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20revise%20the%20concepts.%20This%20time%2C%20I%20learnt%20my%20lesson%20and%20prepared%20clear%20notes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4)%20Practice%20with%20previous%20year%20questions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20consistently%20practiced%20the%20previous%2010%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20papers%20multiple%20times%20to%20sharpen%20his%20answer-writing%20skills%20and%20get%20himself%20accustomed%20to%20the%20exam%20pattern.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20practice%20not%20only%20familiarised%20me%20with%20the%20exam%20pattern%20but%20also%20honed%20my%20real-time%20answer%20writing%20abilities%2C%20which%20is%20crucial%20for%20performing%20well%20in%20the%20mains%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5)%20Value%20addition%20through%20case%20studies%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollecting%20case%20studies%20and%20integrating%20them%20into%20his%20answers%20was%20a%20strategy%20Ajay%20used%20to%20add%20depth%20and%20differentiate%20his%20answers%20in%20optional%20papers%20from%20General%20Studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20a%20conscious%20effort%20to%20understand%20where%20and%20how%20to%20apply%20anthropological%20theories%20in%20different%20contexts.%20This%20involved%20thinking%20about%20possible%20scenarios%20and%20jotting%20down%20topics%20where%20these%20theories%20could%20be%20relevant.%20This%2C%20he%20says%2C%20enhanced%20the%20quality%20of%20his%20answers.%20%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20checking%20notes%20from%20previous%20toppers%20helped%20in%20deriving%20innovative%20ideas%20for%20value%20addition%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6)%20Rigorous%20answer%20writing%20practice%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevoting%20two%20hours%20daily%20to%20practice%20answer%20writing%20was%20a%20non-negotiable%20part%20of%20Ajay%E2%80%99s%20preparation.%20He%20focussed%20on%20writing%208-10%20answers%20each%20day%20across%20various%20question%20types%20(10%2C%2015%2C%20and%2020%20marker%20questions).%20Weekly%20tests%20were%20a%20staple%20in%20his%20routine%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20simulate%20exam%20conditions%20and%20manage%20his%20time%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7)%20Enhance%20presentation%20skills%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20also%20used%20diagrams%2C%20such%20as%20human%20skeletal%20structures%2C%20to%20enhance%20his%20answers%20in%20questions%20related%20to%20anthropological%20studies.%20These%20creative%20presentations%20added%20an%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20Ajay%20successfully%20cleared%20the%20prestigious%20UPSC%20CSE%2C%20securing%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%20705.%20Now%20an%20Indian%20Revenue%20Service%20officer%2C%20he%20eagerly%20awaits%20his%20journey%20to%20the%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20National%20Academy%20of%20Administration%20(LBSNAA)%20in%20Mussoorie%20for%20his%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20courtesy%20Ajay%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751466600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FAjay-IRS-upsc-cse-3-1751458710.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D460341%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20peers%20advising%20against%20it%2C%20Haryana-based%20Ajay%20switched%20his%20UPSC%20optional%20due%20to%20persistent%20low%20scores.%20Anthropology%20offered%20a%20concise%2C%20defined%20syllabus%2C%20predictability%2C%20personal%20interest%2C%20and%20a%20multidisciplinary%20appeal.%20The%20IRS%20officer%20shares%20seven%20ultimate%20tips%20for%20anthropology%20aspirants.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F460341%2Fharyana-ajay-irs-officer-shares-tips-mistakes-of-selecting-upsc-optional-anthropology-startegy%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Deaths%20in%20Gaza%20rise%20significantly%20when%20a%20controversial%20group%20distributes%20aid%2C%20analysis%20reveals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751464440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F07%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-dandf-teaser-aid_6955653.jpg%3F20250702172834%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frise-in-gaza-deaths-linked-to-aid-distributions-by-controversial-group-13391481%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sky%20News%20analysis%20shows%20that%20aid%20distributions%20by%20the%20Gaza%20Humanitarian%20Foundation%20(GHF)%20are%20associated%20with%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20deaths.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frise-in-gaza-deaths-linked-to-aid-distributions-by-controversial-group-13391481%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20Ancient%20Farming%20Method%20Turns%20Floods%20Into%20Food%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENestled%20in%20the%20tranquil%20rain-shadowed%20folds%20of%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20Phek%20district%20lies%20Kikruma%20village.%20Here%2C%20the%20villagers%20practice%20a%20method%20of%20farming%20that%20has%20astounded%20agricultural%20enthusiasts%20for%20generations%3A%20Zabo%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20locally%20as%20the%20Ruza%20system%2C%20this%20ancient%20farming%20practice%20holds%20the%20secret%20not%20only%20to%20overcoming%20monsoon%20flooding%20but%20to%20fostering%20a%20symbiotic%20relationship%20with%20nature.%20The%20system%20was%20developed%20by%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20Chakhesang%20tribe%20in%20Kikruma%20village.%20Evolved%20over%2080-100%20years%2C%20it%20ingeniously%20integrates%20farming%20and%20water%20management%20to%20conserve%20and%20use%20runoff%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20does%20this%20system%2C%20seemingly%20simple%20yet%20brilliantly%20executed%2C%20accomplish%20such%20feats%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20triple-tiered%20strategy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20Zabo%20refers%20specifically%20to%20a%20small%20pit%20within%20a%20paddy%20field%2C%20often%20used%20for%20fish%20rearing.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Ruza%20denotes%20a%20much%20larger%20pond%2C%20typically%20around%20point%20two%20hectares%20in%20size%2C%20designed%20to%20store%20run-off%20water%20from%20the%20upper%20slopes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ruza%20system%20is%20a%20triad%20of%20thriving%20forestry%20at%20hilltops%2C%20productive%20agriculture%20in%20the%20mid-section%2C%20and%20flourishing%20paddy%20fields%20below.%20The%20upper%20tier%20protects%20village%20forestland%2C%20maintaining%20biodiversity%20and%20water%20catchment.%20In%20the%20middle%20tier%2C%20the%20ponds%20and%20cattle%20yards%20synergise%20to%20nurture%20the%20fields%20below%2C%20which%20not%20only%20yield%20rice%20but%20also%20support%20fish%20rearing%20%E2%80%94%20a%20nutritious%20bonus%20that%20enriches%20the%20village%E2%80%99s%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(see%20figure)%20Schematic%20diagram%20of%20the%20Zabo%20farming%20system%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Schematic%20diagram%20of%20Zabo%20farming%20system.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flh7-rt.googleusercontent.com%2Fdocsz%2FAD_4nXe1ucv8b2-al_vOzVWweS-dSux--5KbTS28XhsegzN1cVAE96PxTRMxThM400yLOCfcv41azq35p0kDiFY2dP_NXGQXK1Ka8buAFJOdwstqVbP24rGc8Wnh_YS7Ws7Uvy6TZ4sV%3Fkey%3DJro5jQ19UXkFaRzOGjeFhw%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESchematic%20diagram%20of%20the%20Zabo%20farming%20system.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canr.msu.edu%2F%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.canr.msu.edu%2F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDelving%20into%20Zabo%3A%20The%20art%20of%20water%20management%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Zabo%20system%20begins%20with%20capturing%20rainwater%20from%20hilltops%20and%20forests.%20This%20runoff%20is%20managed%20by%20gravity%20to%20flow%20through%20a%20carefully%20constructed%20network%20of%20small%20channels.%20These%20water%20channels%2C%20meandering%20through%20Kikruma%E2%80%99s%20landscape%2C%20are%20meticulously%20designed%20to%20guide%20the%20rainwater%20into%20strategically%20placed%20ponds%20on%20terraced%20hillsides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20any%20ponds%3B%20they%E2%80%99re%20reservoirs%20carefully%20crafted%20with%20rammed%20earth.%20These%20ponds%20are%20dug%20out%20at%20different%20levels%20on%20terraced%20hillsides%20and%20are%20strategically%20located%20near%20fields%20to%20ease%20the%20process%20of%20irrigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stored%20water%20is%20released%20slowly%20from%20the%20ponds%20for%20irrigation%20purposes.%20This%20gradual%20release%20controls%20water%20flow%20and%20prevents%20sudden%20surges%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F446407%2Fscience-behind-why-northeast-india-receives-heavy-rainfall%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecould%20otherwise%20cause%20flooding%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20channels%20that%20supply%20the%20ponds%20have%20dual%20purposes%20%E2%80%94%20they%20collect%20not%20only%20the%20precious%20rainwater%20but%20also%20nutrients%20from%20cattle%20yards.%20As%20the%20water%20passes%20through%20th