C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EZabo%20versus%20conventional%20farming%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZabo%20stands%20out%20strikingly%20when%20compared%20to%20modern%20monocropping%20or%20slash%E2%80%91and%E2%80%91burn%20systems%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIntegrated%20productivity%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20Zabo%20blends%20forestry%2C%20horticulture%2C%20livestock%2C%20paddy%2C%20and%20fish%20farming%20in%20one%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENatural%20fertilisation%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3ERunoff%20channels%20transport%20cattle%20dung%20and%20urine%20directly%20to%20rice%20fields%2C%20reducing%20the%20need%20for%20chemical%20fertilisers%20and%20enhancing%20soil%20fertility%20sustainably.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWater%20efficiency%20and%20erosion%20control%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F414904%2Fworld-water-day-meghalaya-woman-made-village-self-sufficient-in-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERain%20capture%20in%20sealed%20rammed-earth%20ponds%20%3C%2Fa%3Elimits%20seepage%2C%20prevents%20flash%20floods%2C%20and%20preserves%20soils%2C%20unlike%20conventional%20methods%20that%20often%20result%20in%20erosion%20and%20nutrient%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESustainability%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3EZabo%20relies%20entirely%20on%20passive%20water%20flow%2C%20without%20pumps%20or%20electricity.%20It%20preserves%20biodiversity%2C%20maintains%20medicinal%20plant%20diversity%20on%20pond%20bunds%2C%20and%20aligns%20with%20organic%20principles%20by%20minimising%20external%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECentral%20to%20the%20success%20of%20Zabo%20farming%20is%20the%20community%20spirit%20that%20unites%20the%20people%20of%20Kikruma.%20Each%20family%20pitches%20in%20to%20build%20and%20maintain%20the%20water%20channels%20and%20ponds.%20This%20ensures%20that%20water%20is%20shared%20fairly%2C%20and%20both%20duties%20and%20benefits%20are%20distributed%20equally.%20This%20team%20effort%20turns%20the%20farming%20techn