%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20observed%20the%20growing%20health%20issues%20tied%20to%20poor%20diets%20and%20inactive%20lifestyles%2C%20they%20also%20became%20increasingly%20aware%20of%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20organic%20farmers%20in%20securing%20reliable%20markets%20for%20their%20produce.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20profit%2C%20but%20about%20making%20a%20genuine%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pavani%20reflects.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20believed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356941%2Forganic-farming-mba-grad-earns-crores-earthy-tales-delhi-ncr-deepak-sabharwal-rajasthan-farm-pesticides%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20be%20the%20solution%2C%20not%20only%20for%20the%20health%20of%20consumers%20but%20also%20for%20the%20farmers%20committed%20to%20sustainable%20practices.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20IT%20offices%20to%20farm%20fields%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20prior%20experience%20in%20farming%2C%20Manikanta%20and%20Pavani%20embarked%20on%20an%20intense%20learning%20journey.%20They%20enrolled%20in%20the%20Subash%20Palekar%20Natural%20Farming%20(SPNF)%20method%2C%20a%20technique%20that%20focuses%20on%20sustainability%20and%20eliminates%20the%20use%20of%20chemicals%20and%20pesticides.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20attending%20training%20sessions%20on%20weekends%20in%20our%20village%2C%20Lachannagudipudi%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20while%20working%20in%20Chennai%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manikanta.%20%E2%80%9CBalancing%20our%20full-time%20IT%20jobs%20and%20weekend%20training%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy%2C%20but%20our%20passion%20for%20making%20a%20change%20kept%20us%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20after%20months%20of%20rigorous%20learning%20and%20careful%20planning%2C%20the%20couple%20made%20a%20life-changing%20decision.%20They%20left%20their%20stable%20IT%20careers%20behind%20and%20returned%20to%20Guntur%2C%20investing%20their%20savings%20of%20Rs%2017%20lakh%20into%20a%20new%20venture%2C%20%E2%80%98Sreshte%E2%80%99.%20The%20name%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20Sanskrit%20word%20meaning%20%E2%80%9Cbest%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cexcellent%E2%80%9D%2C%20perfectly%20encapsulated%20their%20vision%2C%20to%20offer%20only%20the%20finest%20organic%20products%2C%20grounded%20in%20their%20commitment%20to%20health%2C%20sustainability%2C%20and%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-500x375.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202017%2C%20Kotinaga%20Manikanta%20and%20Naga%20Venkata%20Durga%20Pavani%20returned%20to%20Guntur%20to%20establish%20Sreshte%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.