uploads%2F2025%2F06%2FThe-Patades-with-Hydrosol-freshener_12_11zon-1751287687-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FThe-Patades-with-Hydrosol-freshener_12_11zon-1751287687-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FThe-Patades-with-Hydrosol-freshener_12_11zon-1751287687-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FThe-Patades-with-Hydrosol-freshener_12_11zon-1751287687-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458389%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20encouragement%20from%20his%20wife%20Priyanka%2C%20a%20plant%20biotechnologist%2C%20Lokesh%20leaped%20at%2035%2C%20investing%20Rs%2080%2C000%20to%20plant%20his%20first%20geranium.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Lokesh%E2%80%99s%20impact%20goes%20beyond%20his%20fields.%20Through%20workshops%2C%20digital%20platforms%2C%20and%20good%20old-fashioned%20word%20of%20mouth%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20inspiring%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20farmers%20to%20embrace%20high-value%20crops%20and%20smart%20agriculture.%20The%20numbers%20speak%20for%20themselves%3A%20while%20India%20consumes%20around%20149%20tons%20of%20geranium%20oil%20annually%2C%20it%20produces%20only%20about%20five%20tons%2C%20leaving%20a%20vast%20market%20wide%20open%20for%20enterprising%20growers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGeranium%20farming%3A%20A%20low-%20maintenance%2C%20high-return%20opportunity%20for%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh-Value%20Crop%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Geranium%20offers%20a%20significant%20income%20opportunity%20for%20farmers%20due%20to%20its%20high%20market%20value.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMultiple%20Oil%20Sources%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Oil%20can%20be%20easily%20extracted%20from%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20%3Cstrong%3Estems%2C%20leaves%2C%20and%20flowers%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELong-Term%20Yield%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Once%20planted%2C%20geranium%20can%20be%20harvested%20for%20%3Cstrong%3Ethree%20to%20four%20years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20reducing%20replanting%20costs.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELow%20Maintenance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20plant%20requires%20%3Cstrong%3Eminimal%20pesticide%20use%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20as%20it%20is%20naturally%20%3Cstrong%3Eresistant%20to%20pests%20and%20grazing%20animals%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigher%20Returns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Yields%20%3Cstrong%3Emuch%20higher%20profits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20compared%20to%20many%20traditional%20crops.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESustainable%20Livelihood%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Promoting%20geranium%20farming%20could%20help%20farmers%20%3Cstrong%3Eincrease%20income%20and%20financial%20stability%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeranium%20was%20first%20introduced%20in%20the%20temperate%20regions%20of%20South%20India%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20Nilgiris%20(Tamil%20Nadu)%2C%20parts%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20due%20to%20their%20suitable%20climate.%20A%20medicinal%20and%20aromatic%20plant%2C%20it%20is%20not%20eaten%20by%20animals%20and%20rarely%20attacked%20by%20pests.%20Its%20leaves%20start%20to%20grow%20shortly%20after%20harvest%2C%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F403491%2Fharyana-techie-and-wife-launch-successful-morina-business-organic-farming-improving-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20farmers%20can%20easily%20earn%20more%20profit%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeranium%20is%20valued%20for%20its%20leaves%2C%20which%20are%20processed%20to%20extract%20essential%20oil.%20This%20oil%20is%20in%20high%20demand%20both%20in%20India%20and%20internationally.%20Once%20planted%2C%20geranium%20can%20be%20harv