%2C%20cost-effective%20solution%20developed%20by%20CSIR-NEERI%20(Council%20of%20Scientific%20and%20Industrial%20Research%20%E2%80%93%20National%20Environmental%20Engineering%20Research%20Institute).%20It%20was%20designed%20to%20restore%20and%20rejuvenate%20degraded%20or%20contaminated%20lands%2C%20particularly%20those%20affected%20by%20fly%20ash%2C%20heavy%20metals%2C%20or%20industrial%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-24_11zon-1751358687.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Singh%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20cleaning%20the%20land%20to%20watering%20the%20bamboo%20trees%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20site%2C%20we%20have%2020%20women%20employed.%20All%20these%20women%20are%20employed%20on%20a%20three-year%20contract.%E2%80%9D%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-24_11zon-1751358687.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-24_11zon-1751358687-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-24_11zon-1751358687-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-24_11zon-1751358687-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-24_11zon-1751358687-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-459051%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Singh%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20cleaning%20the%20land%20to%20watering%20the%20bamboo%20trees%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20site%2C%20we%20have%2020%20women%20employed.%20All%20these%20women%20are%20employed%20on%20a%20three-year%20contract.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ffigcaptio