-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-1-1751288580.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Mitti%20Ka%20Ghar%20restoration%20process%20will%20take%20four%20months%20and%20a%20budget%20of%20over%2040%20lakhs%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-1-1751288580.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-1-1751288580-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-1-1751288580-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-1-1751288580-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-1-1751288580-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458419%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Mitti%20Ka%20Ghar%20restoration%20process%20will%20take%20four%20months%20and%20a%20budget%20of%20over%2040%20lakhs%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mud%20school%20is%20an%20endeavour%20by%20Bhopal-based%20%E2%80%98NGO%20Muskaan%E2%80%99%20that%20focuses%20its%20energies%20on%20informal%20urban%20settlements%20and%20villages%2C%20particularly%20de-notified%20tribes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20education%20becomes%20a%20tool%20for%20change.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESounds%20brilliant%2C%20right%3F%20But%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20problem.%20Muskaan%20is%20uncertain%20how%20much%20longer%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20continue.%20The%20Mitti%20Ka%20Ghar%2C%20you%20see%2C%20needs%20restoration.%20And%20that%20needs%20you.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20read%20this%2C%20a%20team%20of%20architects%20is%20hard%20at%20work%2C%20racing%20a