roblem%2C%20but%20the%20water%20coming%20from%20the%20ground.%20Tackling%20the%20solution%20requires%20a%20vetting%20of%20the%20foundation%2C%20which%20is%20where%20the%20expense%20lies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20will%20take%20four%20months%20to%20complete%2C%20but%20funding%20can%20speed%20it%20up%20significantly.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20school%20is%20large%3B%20the%20built-up%20area%20is%20around%207%2C500%20sq%20ft.%20The%20entire%20cost%20of%20the%20project%20will%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%2045%20lakh%2C%20with%20the%20first%20phase%20amounting%20to%20Rs%2025%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sourabh%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20210%20students%20study%20at%20Muskaan.%20This%20project%20will%20help%20them%20continue%20their%20education.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20success%20isn%E2%80%99t%20measured%20in%20a%20single%20parameter%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Mitti%20Ka%20Ghar%2C%20the%20thrum%20of%20the%20outside%20world%20melts%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20the%20formula%20is%20bent%2C%20enabling%20children%20to%20study%20skills%20and%20concepts%20that%20will%20not%20just%20hold%20in%20good%20stead%20for%20the%20upcoming%20exams%2C%20but%20also%20for%20life.%20As%20Shivani%20Taneja%2C%20founder%20of%20Muskaan%2C%20shares%2C%20in%201997%2C%20when%20she%20started%20out%2C%20intending%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F395350%2Fthis-17-yo-is-empowering-marginalised-students-tackling-textile-waste-creating-jobs-for-the-underprivileged%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenrol%20marginalised%20children%20in%20the%20formal%20schooling%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20realised%20the%20need%20for%20a%20slightly%20different%20approach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebe